🪜 Task 4: IAM Setup for Alex

Scenario Requirements:

✅ View EC2 instances only
✅ Create S3 buckets
❌ Cannot modify EC2

🔐 Custom IAM Policy for Alex

Create policy:
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "ec2:Describe*"
      ],
      "Resource": "*"
    },
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:CreateBucket"
      ],
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}






